name: Test Case 18 : All Review Videos Playing Or Not
descriptionHtml:
Test Case Description:

Validate that all the clinte review videos are present and it is playing in the clinte review page?

Expeceted Results:

All the clinte reviews videos should be present and if we click on that it should play in the clinte reviews page.
